    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, premium driving experience. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though it shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, such as small stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery is intact and supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car has been well-cared for with a documented service history, including a recent comprehensive fluid flush and brake pad replacement. The engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with plenty of tread remaining, ensuring it is road-ready from day one. This is a solid, honest car that delivers comfort and performance in equal measure.",
      "price": 29800.0,
