      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for real-time damping adjustments. This example features the weight-reducing carbon fiber roof, lowering the center of gravity for improved lateral acceleration. Mechanically robust with recent rod bearing preventative maintenance and a fresh throttle actuator service, it presents in honest condition with minor cosmetic wear consistent with its enthusiast pedigree. It offers a visceral, analog driving experience that remains a benchmark in hydraulic steering feedback and linear power delivery.",
